node.text:
#ThrowbackTuesday with the Story of a Dream. For Art Basel 2019 @PaganiofMiami celebrated 20 years of the Zonda with one unforgettable activation. From the original Zonda C12 chassis 001 to the Huayra Roadster BC, the entire history of Pagani Automobili was on full display for enthusiasts to revel in. We can’t wait to see what the next chapter holds for this legendary brand. 

#PrestigeImports #PaganiofMiami #TeamPrestige #PaganiAutomobili #Pagani #Zonda #Huayra #Supercars #Hypercars #CarsofInstagram #InstaCars #CarsofInsta #Supercar #Hypercar #Exotics #ExoticCars #ArtBasel #Carlovers

node.text:
Our Miami Vice Exotics & Espresso recap is here! Celebrating automotive icons from the 80s, 90s, & Miami's Art Deco culture, Team Prestige hosted E&E for South Florida to indulge in. With our show packed with enthusiast specs, Prestige Imports showcased car culture at its finest. Huge thank you to everyone who came out to support us, we’ll see you in August for our next Exotics & Espresso!

node.text:
Sculpted in Performance, the Huayra R from @PaganiAutomobili prepares to claim the hypercar podium with great pride & incredible pace. With the R designation, this hypercar is boundless in its limits.

Encompassing courage, respect, speed, performance, freedom, and racing, the Huayra R is on track to be one of Horacio’s greatest.

"Today’s racing cars are focused exclusively on aerodynamics and are largely the product of the wind tunnel. In the 60s and 70s, however, the cars were very fast, certainly dangerous, but beautiful. 

“Prototype sports cars like the Ferrari P4 or the Ford GT40, or the Le Mans cars, had extremely attractive lines, which are still a huge source of inspiration for our cars today. The Porsche 917 is my favourite, with its romantic yet bold shape, which gives the impression of a very fast car. It is beautiful, elegant and timeless.”

From this desire for freedom, and from the experience of the Zonda R and the cars of the past, came the idea of the Huayra R, like a breath of fresh air.” 
-Horacio Pagani

The Huayra R knows no limits. This Pagani Hypercar combines the highest level of automotive engineering & aerodynamics to achieve an unprecedented aesthetic & relentless performance. Learn more by contacting sales@prestigeimports.com today. 

#PrestigeImports #PaganiofMiami #TeamPrestige #PaganiAutomobili #Pagani #HuayraR #Huayra #SculptedinPerformance #ExoticCars #Hypercar

node.text:
When a recently delivered South Florida Sian was in need of a proper hypercar presentation & paint protection, Team Prestige knew that more had to be done. We are ladies & gentlemen, serving ladies & gentlemen. 

Here at Prestige Imports|Lamborghini Miami, we know that quality customer care doesn't stop once a car has arrived. The client is our real employer & Team Prestige understands that luxury for them translates into great ease and comfort. With the stunning 1 of 63 Lamborghini Sian hypercar, the client experience has to be unforgettable. From wrapping the Sian in full PPF with full Ceramic treatment to a personal delivery by our CEO, thoughtful care and attention was spent to create the ultimate goal: customer satisfaction. 

We are enthusiasts at heart & understand how special a moment like this should be. Huge thanks to this Sian’s owner for trusting Lamborghini Miami & Team Prestige to create this monumental moment for you. We treat our clients like family and we can't wait to see what the future brings us. Just another reminder that All Roads Lead to Lamborghini Miami.

#PrestigeImports #LamborghiniMiami #Sian #AllRoadsLeadtoLamborghiniMiami #Hypercar #CarsofInstagram #InstaCars #CarsofInsta #ExoticCars #Cars #AutomobiliLamborghini
